menu "Busybox DNF"

config DNF
	bool "dnf (8 kb)"
	default y
	select RPM
	select RPM2CPIO
	help
	dnf is a high-level package management frontend for RPM-based
	systems. It handles repository management and dependency
	resolution as a frontend to rpm. It includes unique rescue
	features to manually extract packages using built-in utilities
	if the system package manager is broken.

endmenu
